------------------------------------------------------------------------
r8778 | josef | 2007-01-02 13:11:34 +0100 (Di, 02 Jan 2007) | 9 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod-ggz/ggzmod-ggz.c

- run game executables from $PATH if not given as absolute pathnames

This differs from what ggzd does (which runs them from ggzd's module
directory instead). We should probably add the module directory on both
the client and the server to $PATH and then use execvp.

[commit from josef@nada]


