r8678 | josef | 2006-11-27 10:41:30 +0100 (Mo, 27 Nov 2006) | 7 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggz-config/ggz-config.c

- fix deletion of backward-unreferenced sections

The former behaviour was not critical, but it might have required several
ggz-config --check runs. Now a single run really fixes corrupt module
registries.


