r8359 | jdorje | 2006-07-13 22:34:20 +0200 (Do, 13 Jul 2006) | 5 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzcore/server.c

Quick fix - count oursevles as a player on the server even if we aren't in a
room. However this leaves some problems in player counting because room
changes aren't atomic - switching rooms causes the number of players to drop
for a moment while you are between rooms.

