------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6835 | josef | 2005-01-23 12:29:26 +0100 (So, 23 Jan 2005) | 9 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/configure.ac
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/tests/Makefile.am

- do not use @LDADD@ for mingw32, use $(LIBS) instead

Makefile.am's never contain platform specific stuff!
This should always be managed by configure.ac.
LIBS is added automatically so each additional library (like -lm, -lgettext,
-lreadline) should be added here.

For 0.0.11 the windows tests should move out of configure.ac and to m4/*.m4.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6834 | josef | 2005-01-23 12:16:19 +0100 (So, 23 Jan 2005) | 2 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
