------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6724 | jdorje | 2005-01-18 03:51:57 +0100 (Di, 18 Jan 2005) | 4 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/game.c
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/ggzmod.c
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/ggzmod.h

Add a new ggzmod state, CONNECTED.  Go into this state once the ggz client
to game client connection is made, and stay in it until the game server
connection is made (when the state is changed to waiting).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
