------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6717 | oojah | 2005-01-17 02:02:14 +0100 (Mo, 17 Jan 2005) | 4 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   D /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/Makefile.msys.in
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/configure.ac
   D /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/Makefile.msys.in
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/m4/ggz.m4

Removed misguided Makefiles for building dlls on win32.

configure.ac now natively builds dlls with libtool. If you get errors about wsock32 and pthread not being available as shared libraries, you need to update libtool.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6715 | oojah | 2005-01-16 20:10:57 +0100 (So, 16 Jan 2005) | 11 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   A /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/Makefile.msys.in
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/configure.ac
   A /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/Makefile.msys.in

Added new Makefiles for compiling/linking on win32.

Use

make -f Makefile.msys
make -f Makefile.msys install

etc.

This will produce a .dll file and a .a file for linking against.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
