------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4340 | jdorje | 2002-08-07 08:31:34 +0200 (Mi, 07 Aug 2002) | 7 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/ggzmod.c
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/ggzmod.h

Changed the ggzmod interface slightly: the GGZMOD_EVENT_SERVER event now
passes a pointer to the FD (int*) instead of passing the FD directly
(int).

This makes it consistent with the rest of the ggzmod and ggzdmod api's,
as well as more stable overall.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4330 | jdorje | 2002-08-01 06:53:16 +0200 (Do, 01 Aug 2002) | 9 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/configure.in

Exit the configure script if expat-dev is not found; don't just give a
warning and continue.  This makes the process nearly identical to what is
used for ggzd.

Note there are a few problems with this system: (1) ggzmod is linked to
expat (as the game servers are in ggzd); (2) if we're only compiling ggzmod
(or the game servers in ggzd) we shouldn't need expat, and (3) there is no
way (that I know of) to compile just ggzmod (without ggzcore).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
