r3111 | jdorje | 2002-01-14 06:53:06 +0100 (Mo, 14 Jan 2002) | 3 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/Makefile.am
   D /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/ggz_client.h
   M /trunk/ggz/src/ggzcore/ggzcore.h
