------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2209 | jdorje | 2001-08-24 00:01:30 +0200 (Fr, 24 Aug 2001) | 2 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz-client-libs/ggzmod/ggz_client.h

